      "title": "People are still blocking Panchikawatte Road demanding fuel",
      "body_lines": [
        "People in the Panchikawatte area blocked roads for the second day in a row this morning (24) demanding fuel.",
        "People have been waiting in line for several days due to the non-availability of fuel at the Panchikawatte petrol station for several days.",
        "Residents of Panchikawatte also blocked the road yesterday (23) morning, protesting for fuel and causing traffic congestion."
